1
00:00:03,436 --> 00:00:04,670
Ever since the wrap party,

2
00:00:04,671 --> 00:00:06,039
he's just vanished.

3
00:00:07,841 --> 00:00:09,442
Not a single text.

4
00:00:10,410 --> 00:00:12,112
He's busy with promos.

5
00:00:12,645 --> 00:00:14,047
Like I'm not busy too?

6
00:00:15,348 --> 00:00:17,549
I stormed off that day,

7
00:00:17,550 --> 00:00:19,219
so shouldn't he be the one explaining?

8
00:00:19,619 --> 00:00:20,619
But look at him now.

9
00:00:22,288 --> 00:00:24,057
Maybe he's just waiting
for you to cool off.

10
00:00:27,327 --> 00:00:28,761
Fine...

11
00:00:28,762 --> 00:00:30,195
Whatever.

12
00:00:30,196 --> 00:00:31,097
This Hei Yan guy...

13
00:00:31,098 --> 00:00:32,231
he's totally heartless.

14
00:00:32,232 --> 00:00:33,665
He's just using you to climb the ladder.

15
00:00:33,666 --> 00:00:34,401
Am I right?

16
00:00:34,402 --> 00:00:35,835
I'll get a special budget approved

17
00:00:36,102 --> 00:00:37,504
and ruin him, I'm telling you.

18
00:00:42,008 --> 00:00:43,109
This is definitely on you.

19
00:00:43,410 --> 00:00:45,411
You're the one beefing with Lin Bingchen,

20
00:00:45,412 --> 00:00:46,846
so he's having Hei Yan

21
00:00:47,213 --> 00:00:48,213
take it out on me.

22
00:00:49,182 --> 00:00:50,216
It's all your fault.

23
00:00:56,556 --> 00:00:57,791
The teaser is out.

24
00:00:58,258 --> 00:00:59,392
I'll send you the link.

25
00:00:59,793 --> 00:01:01,294
People are loving it!

26
00:01:02,362 --> 00:01:03,463
Loving who?

27
00:01:05,398 --> 00:01:06,833
The "devoted" Hei Yan,

28
00:01:11,571 --> 00:01:13,473
and the "authentic" you.

29
00:01:14,974 --> 00:01:16,008
Take a look.

30
00:01:16,009 --> 00:01:17,043
Come on.

31
00:01:20,647 --> 00:01:22,114
This part is great.

32
00:01:22,115 --> 00:01:23,283
This part too.

33
00:01:25,151 --> 00:01:26,920
But I don't like the angle here.

34
00:01:27,687 --> 00:01:29,288
You both look good.

35
00:01:29,289 --> 00:01:30,422
He's really putting in the effort.

36
00:01:30,423 --> 00:01:31,124
What?

37
00:01:31,324 --> 00:01:32,324
You're not bad either.

38
00:01:32,692 --> 00:01:33,926
You two look great together.

39
00:01:33,927 --> 00:01:35,228
That's why it works.

40
00:01:36,062 --> 00:01:37,663
He's the reason you shine.

41
00:01:37,664 --> 00:01:38,898
I'm the reason he shines!

42
00:01:39,432 --> 00:01:40,499
You're the reason he shines.

43
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:41,500
Fine, fine.

44
00:01:46,005 --> 00:01:46,739
You're "Right,"

45
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:47,773
and I'm "Right" too.

46
00:01:47,774 --> 00:01:49,214
Wearing it on the same right hand...

47
00:01:49,909 --> 00:01:50,777
Tell me,

48
00:01:50,778 --> 00:01:52,412
will we always be like this?

49
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:01,120
I'm asking you one more time.

50
00:02:01,754 --> 00:02:03,056
Do you want to be with me?

51
00:02:04,724 --> 00:02:05,725
Let me see.

52
00:02:06,926 --> 00:02:08,128
That car accident...

53
00:02:08,461 --> 00:02:09,762
was it really serious?

54
00:02:10,263 --> 00:02:11,264
Did it leave a scar?
